descriptionHtml:
So this is a series that I started making, it\'s a story about a wood elf hunter who is hunting with his friend Faendal. In this episode they come across bandits and a mage who seems to be doing some sort of dark ritual.

This is still a work in progress episode, I\'m thinking of adding voice acting and some dialogues. However, I can\'t voice them all by myself so if anyone would be interested in doing some voice acting, send me a pm.
